' =====================================================================
' LEYENDA
' =====================================================================
legend right
  |= Estereotipo |= Significado |
  | <<platform-root>> | Raiz de plataforma, sin _tenant_id |
  | <<core>> | Operacional mutable tenant-scoped |
  | <<append-only>> | Historial inmutable; sin _updated_at ni _deleted |
  | <<event>> | Append-only alto volumen; particionar y archivar |
  | <<versioned>> | valid_from / valid_until o status workflow |
  | <<versioned, append-only>> | Append-only practico; solo cierre tecnico de vigencia |
  | <<snapshot>> | Foto congelada inmutable para auditoria |
  | <<projection>> | Cache derivado; source = eventos |
  | <<catalog>> | Datos de referencia / definiciones |
  | <<platform-shared>> | Cross-tenant, sin _tenant_id |
  | <<privacy>> | Sensible; reglas de minimizacion y retencion |
  | <<derived>> | Calculado y recalculable |
  | <<case>> | Gestion de revision/investigacion |
  | <<quality>> | Reglas y hallazgos de calidad de datos |
  | <<roadmap>> | Alcance de implementacion MVP/Fase 1/Fase 2 |
  | <<yaml-config>> | Configuracion YAML externa, versionada en Git |
  | <<no-orm>> | No crear tabla, entidad ORM ni migracion SQL |
endlegend

